ðŸ”¹1. Cumulative Value Measure (ordered by SpendValue)

CumulativeValue =
CALCULATE(
SUM('YourTable'[Value]),
FILTER(
ALLSELECTED('YourTable'),
'YourTable'[Category] = MAX('YourTable'[Category]) &&
'YourTable'[SpendValue] <= MAX('YourTable'[SpendValue])
)
)

ðŸ”¹2. Total per Category (within filters)

TotalCategoryValue =
CALCULATE(
SUM('YourTable'[Value]),
FILTER(
ALLSELECTED('YourTable'),
'YourTable'[Category] = MAX('YourTable'[Category])
)
)

ðŸ”¹3. Cumulative Percentage Measure

CumulativePct =
DIVIDE([CumulativeValue], [TotalCategoryValue]) * 100